title: University Challenge NZ S15E02
description:
Series 15 Episode 1 - Auckland vs Lincoln

University Challenge was a long-running New Zealand television quiz show. The format was based on the British show of the same name, which was itself based on the American College Bowl. It is currently produced by Cue TV in Invercargill.
Teams consist of five members, each representing a New Zealand university. All eight of the country's universities compete (Auckland, AUT, Canterbury, Massey, Otago, Victoria, Waikato, and Lincoln University)
